The brother of Boney M 's lead singer Liz Mitchell has been arrested in connection with the killing of a Syrian-born imam .
Burnell ` Bernie ' Mitchell - who changed his name to Khalid Rashad after converting to Islam - has been held on suspicion of conspiracy to murder after the death of Abdul Hadi Arwani , a Syrian national .
The 61-year-old has also been arrested on suspicion on preparing and instigating acts of terrorism .
